supportDesc.support:
Written on 112 leaves of good-quality membrane, preceded and followed by a raised paste-down, conjunct respectively with fols. iv and 111. Item 2, a modern sheet of paper, is inserted between fols. i and iv. 

Fore-leaves: fol. irv, text, = 1; fols. iir, iiir, text, = *2; 
                              fols. iiv, iiiv, blank; fol. ivr, names, title; fol. ivv, note.
